---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
---

<Layout title="About - Meowzer Playground">
  <Header />

  <main>
    <article class="about-content">
      <h1>What is this?</h1>
      <p>
        A fun playground for creating and playing with simulated cats!
        üê±
      </p>

      <h2>How to use it</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Click "Create Cat" to make a new friend</li>
        <li>Customize colors, patterns, and personality</li>
        <li>Watch them roam around the screen</li>
        <li>Save your favorites and share them!</li>
      </ol>

      <h2>Credits</h2>
      <p>
        This demo site was built with <a
          href="https://astro.build"
          target="_blank">Astro</a
        >
        and <a href="https://lit.dev" target="_blank">Lit</a> web components.
        Development was assisted by GitHub Copilot using Claude Sonnet 4.5.
      </p>

      <h3>Technical Details</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Framework:</strong>
          <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank">Astro</a>, a
          modern static site generator that enables fast,
          content-focused websites
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Components:</strong>
          <a href="https://lit.dev" target="_blank">Lit</a> web components
          from the <code>@meowzer/ui</code> package for all interactive
          cat functionality
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>State Management:</strong> The <code
            >&lt;meowzer-provider&gt;</code
          > component manages cat state and orchestrates all cat behaviors
          throughout the application
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Styling:</strong> Custom CSS using CSS custom properties
          for theming, ensuring a consistent look across all pages
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Deployment:</strong> Deployed on Netlify with automatic
          builds from the main branch
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="demo-cats">
        <p class="demo-label">
          ‚Üê Some cats roaming on this page too! ‚Üí
        </p>
        <meowzer-provider auto-init>
          <mb-cat-playground></mb-cat-playground>
        </meowzer-provider>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>

<script>
  import "@meowzer/ui/setup";
  import "@meowzer/ui";
</script>

<style>
  main {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  h1 {
    color: var(--accent-orange);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  h2 {
    color: #333;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  h3 {
    color: #444;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  p {
    color: #555;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  ul,
  ol {
    color: #555;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: initial;
  }

  ol {
    list-style: initial;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  code {
    background: #f0f0f0;
    padding: 0.2em 0.4em;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
    color: #333;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--accent-blue);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .demo-cats {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #f9f9f9;
    border-radius: 8px;
    position: relative;
    min-height: 300px;
  }

  .demo-label {
    text-align: center;
    color: #999;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
</style>
